item.title: Operating Systems for ASUS Tinker Board
item.description: In this Article I had collected all available OS for single-board computer ASUS Tinker Board. Based on this computer i will to construct my robot with AI implementation and computer vision. Actually this the first reason why i had select Tinker Board that based on Rockchip RK3288 processor with 4x Cores “Cortex-A17” and work with frequency 1.8 GHz, and support hardware decoding H.265 with resolution 4K х 2К and besides, new chipset get support network 4G LTE with 64-bit RAM LPDDR3.
